file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.1"
info:
  title: "Ministry of Health - Locations of Interest API"
  version: "2021-06-10T02:04:23Z"
servers:
  - url: "https://api.integration.covid19.health.nz/{basePath}"
    variables:
      basePath:
        default: "/loi/v1"
paths:
  /exposure-locations:
    get:
      responses:
        "200":
          description: "200 response"
          headers:
            Strict-Transport-Security:
              schema:
                type: "string"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/MODEL823a48"
components:
  schemas:
    MODEL823a48:
      required:
        - "items"
      type: "object"
      properties:
        items:
          minItems: 1
          uniqueItems: true
          type: "array"
          items:
            required:
              - "endDateTime"
              - "eventId"
              - "eventName"
              - "startDateTime"
            type: "object"
            properties:
              eventId:
                minLength: 1
                type: "string"
              startDateTime:
                minLength: 1
                type: "string"
              eventName:
                minLength: 1
                type: "string"
              location:
                required:
                  - "address"
                type: "object"
                properties:
                  address:
                    minLength: 1
                    type: "string"
              endDateTime:
                minLength: 1
                type: "string"
